{"tid":494102,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(#metoo) 張文慈上《東張》重提遭性侵：講俾人「迷咩」，我面對唔到","createTime":"2017-12-09T09:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T15:05:26.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06d99c5bff432677a79f94246f1eac5cc8e18565","tid":494102,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"性侵風波未息，除咗多位女星先後自爆曾遭性侵，包括索媽陳敏之（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2B5gPnG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2B5gPnG&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cd7a3115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2B5gPnG</a> ）、「十優港姐」麥明詩（新聞連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2AL0zrK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2AL0zrK&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=588546c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2AL0zrK</a> ），仲有被舊事重提嘅張文慈（Pinky）。<br />\n<br />\n張文慈（Pinky）07年接受周刊訪問時，憶述自己17歲嗰年識咗一名男性，初時以為對方係好人，點知遭出賣受傷害，Pinky多年後於教會分享信仰經歷時，重提舊事，她說：「我沒有不開心，沒有喊，只是覺得遺憾！被騙！不是因為失去身體，而是失去那份信任。」<br />\n<br />\n前幾日Pinky出席活動時，也被問及性侵舊事，她亦稱已經忘過去，「我覺得真係要搵信任嘅人講畀佢哋聽，唔係會有更多受害者。」<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，Pinky再接受大台《東張西望》訪問，講咗更多當日案發詳情，訪問昨晚播出。<br />\n<br />\nPinky憶述，當年她做暑期工，認識咗個男同事，事發當日，Pinky跟男同事，和另一位女同事食飯，Pinky強調與該名男同事並非男女朋友關係。<br />\n<br />\nPinky稱該名男同事在其飲品落藥，之後她就失去知覺，醒起時發現自己耳仔同身體都有流血。《東張》主持問佢為何不報警，她稱：「當時冇報警，更加冇諗過要話俾屋企人知，我覺得大鑊喇！講俾屋企人聽死梗喇！講俾朋友聽但幫唔到幾多，我能夠做嘅只係以後唔見呢個男人。其實我好驚，一諗起報警會被人知，我覺得自己好醜，唔敢同人講。」<br />\n<br />\nPinky話入行後無意間提及呢件事，卻換嚟被人話佢博宣傳，而且雖然已經事隔廿幾年，但她稱其實一直以來都未能放低件事，「又唔敢出街，我覺得好醜，最困難係唔知點面對屋企人。」Pinky說到激動處，更眼濕濕謂：「講真，如果要我講呢兩個字出嚟，我覺得好核突囉！就係講俾人『迷咩』（迷姦）呢兩個字，我係面對唔到㗎o依家，我覺得用被人『性侵犯』會比較好，個心會舒服啲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/170225_2f06bf8c19ec14a7f16148489f8aa369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F170225_2f06bf8c19ec14a7f16148489f8aa369.jpg&h=0a1d6567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/170230_186d881d727525ec78c707430d3e5a15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F170230_186d881d727525ec78c707430d3e5a15.jpg&h=1449388f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/170234_592b299e5920779e15e64b718d94b73c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F170234_592b299e5920779e15e64b718d94b73c.jpg&h=f9cff896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/170238_e6f0f37bbfd4f14810c9556d23276830.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F170238_e6f0f37bbfd4f14810c9556d23276830.jpg&h=e3355635&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d5f2c17573c7c8f77500a6b6b9a013f4862aa2f","tid":494102,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:04:33.000Z","msg":"男同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae83f300e3a895b530d1a48a31771c59cecd434","tid":494102,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"嗰個佢條仔嚟㗎仲話唔係，戲子真係戲子"},{"pid":"8c801c02c90d2f2353237d426da6065b6a3ed05a","tid":494102,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"女女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ff5c64c1bed19a894dfb80f4c896493d60d7fe","tid":494102,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"咪又係雞"},{"pid":"55bd434fa5a2e838157d4e3fd90c1242fcf6d8ec","tid":494102,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41f113d8f5a46aa381c6b3d359f3b58864b2815c","tid":494102,"uid":62990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"金未來"},{"pid":"8